      • completeQuery

        public java.lang.String completeQuery​(java.lang.String query,
                                      java.lang.String nameCard,
                                      java.lang.String category,
                                      java.lang.String classCard,
                                      java.lang.String typeCard)
        Based on the parameters inserted, the parameter query is completed
        Parameters:
        query - a String. Indicates query that is going to be modified
        nameCard - a String. Indicates the name of the card searched
        category - a String. Indicates the category of the card searched
        classCard - a String. Indicates the class of the card searched
        typeCard - a String. Indicates the type of the card searched
        Returns:
        String. The final query used in filter methods
